'''''Fortune Global Forum''''' is an annual conference held by ''[[Fortune (magazine)|Fortune]]'' magazine. The first conference was held in [[Singapore]] in 1995.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://biz.cn.yahoo.com/fortunenews/050424/20.html|title=Basic information of Previous Fortune Global Forum|publisher=Yahoo|date=2005-04-24|accessdate=2013-01-15}}</ref> The Fortune Global Forum convenes the presidents, chairmen, CEOs of the world's top companies and also prestigious economists.

The latest forum will take place in [[Guangzhou]], [[China]] in Dec, 2017. The topic is "Openness and Innovation: Shaping the Global Economy".

